app_details.author: BangDB
app_details.name: ShopIQ++
app_details.description:
Whether you're monitoring your online business to increase sales or a B2B company trying to generate more leads, CRM E-Commerce is the perfect App to help you achieve your goals.
The App offers a range of features, including live visitor tracking, powerful insight, website forms tracking, custom patterns to score leads, real-time notifications, and leads management, making it the perfect solution for businesses.
app_details.short_intro: The App helps you to understand whats happening in online business and get insights on whats working and whats not. You can track the behavior of  visitors, gain insights into their interests, and use that data to optimize your website for better engagement and conversions.
